{"tid":542112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你條見異思遷既仆街","createTime":"2018-01-27T07:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T00:00:57.000Z","uid":168989,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"90cff96b03c6b2ec05657d960d0d9a9d862f13d3","tid":542112,"uid":168989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"我同ex係ig識，傾左兩星期就約出黎，約左幾次就一齊左。<br />\n我地見過大家既朋友，佢呀爸呀媽都知道我既存在。<br />\n<br />\n佢追我果時就反應熱烈。<br />\n追到手後，熱戀期得2星期，whatsapp覆得勁慢，最耐半日之後先覆，一至兩星期先見一次。<br />\n拍緊拖同單身冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熱戀期時，一星期見4次，仲會秒回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩冇發生關係，如果唔係仲hurt<br />\n<br />\n其實佢咁冷淡，我都有分手既念頭。<br />\n但諗住岩岩先一齊，大家一齊磨合下，可能遲啲會有改進。<br />\n佢真係有改，但好快打回原形，仲變本加厲。<br />\n當我再提下佢，佢就提出分手。<br />\n我求佢都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢變本加厲前去左christmas ball。<br />\n之後我見到佢係ig follow左個女仔。<br />\n條女都有去果個christmas ball。<br />\n<br />\n分左手後，佢block左我ig, snapchat，unfriend我fb。<br />\n<br />\n我肯定佢冇比帽我戴，因為佢仲係單身。<br />\n但有機會中意左果個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我用第二個ig 見到佢狂聊條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到有人問佢有冇中意既人，佢答有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢一定係ig狂搵條女，好似當初佢咁聊我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我dllm，分左手1個月，竟然咁快放得低，一啲思念都冇？<br />\n枉我送左個$1000既袋比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個月就變心真係好荒謬。<br />\n可能你只係貪新鮮感。<br />\n不過分得好，比我快啲睇清原來你係對感情唔認真既渣男<br />\n見異思遷既人根本唔識愛人，連尊重人都唔識。<br />\n學乜人拍拖？你不配！<br />\n唔好再害人啦，你實有報應！<br />\n騎牛搵馬既人開頭永遠都會話自己係認真。<br />\n岩岩一齊千奇唔好100%付出，否則就會比佢食住，受傷果個一定係自己<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果你真係中意個女仔，溝佢時，唔好好似你呃我咁 呃佢話你冇食煙。其實聞到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到呢個post，唔好嬲，因為我冇開你名已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps: A1的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a442851727c7ee25988c7e7298c6b1fab4d1a80","tid":542112,"uid":57643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"ig點識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亂咁direct人？"},{"pid":"f9b5a251e60a0b066688c3592cd829fa0b804eaa","tid":542112,"uid":168989,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a442851727c7ee25988c7e7298c6b1fab4d1a80","tid":542112,"uid":57643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"ig點識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亂咁direct人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"係direct人呀。<br />\n有機會係女就direct<br />\n睇下邊個快得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4888f11cc888cf9b6dbb08f7979995578bdd4301","tid":542112,"uid":57643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f9b5a251e60a0b066688c3592cd829fa0b804eaa","tid":542112,"uid":168989,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a442851727c7ee25988c7e7298c6b1fab4d1a80","tid":542112,"uid":57643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"ig點識人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亂咁direct人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"係direct人呀。<br />\n有機會係女就direct<br />\n睇下邊個快得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁正常direct得你既，都會direct第二個<br />\n咪當買個經驗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝你下個更可愛"},{"pid":"f1f2a2523668e6dfb5c2d7a0137ede7c45b5118f","tid":542112,"uid":168989,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4888f11cc888cf9b6dbb08f7979995578bdd4301","tid":542112,"uid":57643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f9b5a251e60a0b0666